{
  "stem": "3085.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was considered the best high school in Pecs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it wasn't very pleasant in some ways because obviously, being Jewish in a-- in a-- in a Catholic school, strictly Catholic school, it had its disadvantages.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were not, in fact-- we were not, in fact, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] proper students.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- we were considered external students to, to school because we were not allowed to be enrolled as regular students in, in, in, in that gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I recall, at the end of the first term, or first-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] excuse me-- at the end of the first term-- [DRINKS] the first year of school 1944, just before we were deported, we had to go to exams in that school with our yellow star badge on our Hungarian national uniform, which was pretty incongruous, [LAUGHS] to say the least.",
      "word_count": 68
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I recall that I think the priests were more embarrassed than we were, seeing us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not sure if they were embarrassed to see us with the yellow Star of David.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think they were embarrassed because the yellow Star of David was on the national uniform of the school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and that, that was-- that, that was, I-- I think, very objectionable to them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But again, I-- just like in any group of people, you had some priests who were more sympathetic.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there were some who were less sympathetic to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some were probably almost openly anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Others were very, very kind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, and so you, you can't really generalize in even in a small group as, as maybe a dozen or two dozen teachers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
